{{nihongo|I '''Yukio Mishima'''|三島 由紀夫|Mishima Yukio}} ing talipampan nang  {{nihongo|'''Kimitake Hiraoka'''|平岡 公威|Hiraoka Kimitake|extra=Enero 14, 1925{{spaced ndash}}November 25, 1970}}, metung a talasulat, poeta, talasulat drama, artista, ampong direktor da reng pelikula. Mekatatlu ya mimunikala o me-nomina para king [[Galal a Nobel Para king Malagung Panyulat o Literatura]] i Mishima, a tuturing dang metung kareng pekamaulagang talasulat a Hapon king kadwang pulung siglu o dilanwa. Makalto king kayang obrang [[avant-garde]] ing pamiyabe ning paglalaweng tradisyunal ampong makabayu, a memalbal kareng angganan a mibakud uli ning kultura, a makatutuk king seksuwalidad, kamatayan ampong pamagbayu king pulitika.<ref>http://www.enotes.com/twentieth-century-criticism/mishima-yukio</ref> Tatandanan de murin uling king kayang ritwal a pamagpakamate kapamilitan ning ''[[seppuku]]'' kaybat nang mebigu ning kayang tangkang ''[[coup d'état]]''.

